event.title: Get Your HP Printer Setup Hands-freely At 123.hp/setup
event.description: To bring your HP printer setup, you need to give a click at 123.hp.com/setup by opening a web browser on your computer system. The effectual and hands-free solution is there, you only have to follow the guidelines as mentioned on that page. Once you reach to the bottom of the page, you will see your HP printer has been setup.
